description: The Radxa CM3J is an industrial-grade compute module built around the Rockchip RK3568J SoC. This compact module integrates a CPU, PMU, LPDDR4X, eMMC, and wireless connectivity options such as Wi-Fi 5 and Bluetooth 5.0 in a 55mm x 40mm form factor. title: Radxa CM3J with Built-in Wi-Fi 5 and Bluetooth 5.0 for Industrial Applications

description: MediaTek continues to strengthen upstream support for its Genio IoT platforms through its collaboration with Collabora. title: Expanding Open-Source Support for MediaTek’s Genio IoT Platforms with Collabora
